  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bc8 \u0ba8\u0bcb\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc0\u0ba9 \u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0b87\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc8 \u0b95\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Indian Navy monitors the movement of a Chinese ship bound for Sri Lanka",
      "author": "Rajeeban",
      "body_lines": [
        "Indian security sources have informed the print that they are monitoring the movement of a Chinese ship traveling towards Sri Lanka.",
        "Security sources said that the movement of a Chinese research vessel bound for Sri Lanka's Ambandottai port was being monitored.",
        "The Indian Navy is monitoring the movement of a Chinese ship bound for Sri Lanka's Ambandottai port",
        "Security sources said that the destination of the ship is not known.",
        "Defense officials have said that such ships will start departing when China or any other country conducts missile tests. They have said that this is not a warship, and we have observed that such ships have moved in this area before.",
        "China's research vessel Yuanwang 5 is engaged in space and satellite surveillance. Sri Lanka's Ministry of Defense, which initially denied the arrival of the particular ship, later confirmed that the ship will dock at Ambantota port between 11th and 17th.",
        "Sri Lanka said this after Indian External Affairs Ministry Spokesperson Arindam Pakshi told the media that India is closely monitoring issues that may affect its security and economic interests."
      ],
